WEBVTT

00:01.251 --> 00:03.627
James Green? You're hereby
placed under arrest.

00:03.795 --> 00:05.295
The vacant
executive officer position?

00:05.463 --> 00:07.881
My recommendation will be
to appoint Dr. Foster.

00:08.048 --> 00:08.924
What?

00:09.092 --> 00:11.093
Leave with me.
I can't.

00:11.261 --> 00:12.845
I's waiting
for my Gabriel.

00:13.013 --> 00:14.513
That hospital
you have access to --

00:14.681 --> 00:17.766
we're going to blow that place
to kingdom come.

